    "1": {
      "title": "Arrows",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Arrows\">Arrows</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Arcane_Archer_Pack_Items&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Arrows\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"notice-default vmid\" style=\"background-color:#EEEEFF;border-color:#AAAAFF;text-align:center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:100%\"><b>This page or section is incomplete.  You can help by adding to it.</b><br />Fire and lightning arrows may ignore resistances, needs testing; values need to be confirmed after December 2018 update (specifically the elemental damage for elemental arrows)<br /><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">For more information, see the <a href=\"/wiki/Help:Contents\" title=\"Help:Contents\">help files</a>, the <a href=\"/wiki/UESPWiki:Style_Guide\" title=\"UESPWiki:Style Guide\">style guide</a>, and this article's <span class=\"plainlinks\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.uesp.net/wiki/Skyrim_talk:Arcane_Archer_Pack_Items\">talk page</a></span>.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Damage\"><img alt=\"Damage\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/22px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/33px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/44px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Enchantment/Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d4/SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d4/SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d4/SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-Firewood.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Firewood\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Firewood\">Firewood</a>\n</th>\n<th>Other\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis_Arrow.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis Arrow.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis_Arrow.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis_Arrow.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis_Arrow.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis_Arrow.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis_Arrow.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Telekinesis_Arrow.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Telekinesis_Arrow\"></span>Telekinesis Arrow<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">800</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>111\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">1</td>\n<td>2 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Void_Salts\" title=\"Skyrim:Void Salts\">Void Salts</a><br /> Makes 10 arrows\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><i>Remains suspended in the air until released using the Lesser Power \"Telekinesis Arrows\".</i>\n<ul><li>Controlled via the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Telekinesis_Arrows\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Telekinesis Arrows\">Telekinesis Arrows</a> Lesser Power</li>\n<li>Can be crafted upon picking up <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Telekinesis_Arrows_Research_Notes\" title=\"Skyrim:Telekinesis Arrows Research Notes\">Telekinesis Arrows Research Notes</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:The_Arcanaeum\" title=\"Skyrim:The Arcanaeum\">the Arcanaeum</a></li>\n<li>These arrows originally had a damage value of 10 before an update for Arcane Archer Pack was released in December 2018. The arrows were changed from a damage value of 30 to 111 in the Anniversary Edition Update.</li>\n<li>Some NPCS may be equipped with Telekinesis Arrow that the player can't obtain, It can be fired as a regular arrow.</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Soul_Stealer_Arrow.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Soul Stealer Arrow.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ee/SR-icon-weapon-Soul_Stealer_Arrow.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Soul_Stealer_Arrow.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ee/SR-icon-weapon-Soul_Stealer_Arrow.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Soul_Stealer_Arrow.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ee/SR-icon-weapon-Soul_Stealer_Arrow.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Soul_Stealer_Arrow.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Soul_Stealer_Arrow\"></span>Soul Stealer Arrow<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">801</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>14\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">1</td>\n<td>10 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Soul_Gem_Arrowhead\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Soul Gem Arrowhead\">Soul Gem Arrowheads</a><br /> Makes 10 arrows\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><i>On a lethal blow, manifests itself into a soul gem filled with the soul of the target.</i>\n<ul><li>Soulsteal, 1 point\n<ul><li>When a non-essential, non-invulnerable NPC is killed, adds a leveled filled soul gem to its inventory.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Can be crafted upon picking up the Soul Stealer Arrows in <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Kagrumez\" title=\"Skyrim:Kagrumez\">Kagrumez</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Fire_Arrows.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Fire Arrows.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/e7/SR-icon-weapon-Fire_Arrows.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Fire_Arrows.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/e7/SR-icon-weapon-Fire_Arrows.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Fire_Arrows.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/e/e7/SR-icon-weapon-Fire_Arrows.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Fire_Arrows.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Fire_Arrow\"></span>Fire Arrow<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">802</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>8\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">1</td>\n<td>4 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Fire_Salts\" title=\"Skyrim:Fire Salts\">Fire Salts</a><br /> Makes 10 arrows\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">\n<ul><li>2 points of damage</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Fire_Damage\" title=\"Skyrim:Fire Damage\">Fire Damage</a>, 40 points</li>\n<li>Will ignite oil-based <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Traps\" title=\"Skyrim:Traps\">traps</a> with Version 1.6 of the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Special_Edition_Patch\" title=\"Skyrim:Special Edition Patch\">Official Skyrim Special Edition Patch</a>.</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Ice_Arrows.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Ice Arrows.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d0/SR-icon-weapon-Ice_Arrows.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Ice_Arrows.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d0/SR-icon-weapon-Ice_Arrows.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Ice_Arrows.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d0/SR-icon-weapon-Ice_Arrows.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Ice_Arrows.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Ice_Arrow\"></span>Ice Arrow<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">803</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>8\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">1</td>\n<td>4 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Frost_Salts\" title=\"Skyrim:Frost Salts\">Frost Salts</a><br /> Makes 10 arrows\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Slow\" title=\"Skyrim:Slow\">Slow</a>, 50 points for 5 seconds</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Frost_Damage\" title=\"Skyrim:Frost Damage\">Frost Damage</a>, 40 points</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Lightning_Arrows.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Lightning Arrows.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2e/SR-icon-weapon-Lightning_Arrows.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Lightning_Arrows.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2e/SR-icon-weapon-Lightning_Arrows.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Lightning_Arrows.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2e/SR-icon-weapon-Lightning_Arrows.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Lightning_Arrows.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Lightning_Arrow\"></span>Lightning Arrow<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">804</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>8\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">1</td>\n<td>4 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Void_Salts\" title=\"Skyrim:Void Salts\">Void Salts</a><br /> Makes 10 arrows\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">\n<ul><li>2 points of damage</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Shock_Damage\" title=\"Skyrim:Shock Damage\">Shock Damage</a>, 40 points</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Bound_Arrow\"></span>Bound Arrow<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">80D</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>32\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"></td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">\n<ul><li>The Mystic version of <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Bound_Arrow\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Bound Arrow\">Bound Arrow</a></li>\n<li>100 are acquired when casting the Bound Quiver spell with the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Mystic_Binding\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Mystic Binding\">Mystic Binding</a> perk unlocked, but will disappear once the spell's duration ends.</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Bone_Arrow.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Bone Arrow.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6a/SR-icon-weapon-Bone_Arrow.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Bone_Arrow.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6a/SR-icon-weapon-Bone_Arrow.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Bone_Arrow.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6a/SR-icon-weapon-Bone_Arrow.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Bone_Arrow.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Bone_Arrow\"></span>Bone Arrow<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">822</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>26\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">1</td>\n<td>10 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dragon_Bone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Dragon Bone\">Dragon Bones</a><br /> Makes 10 arrows\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">\n<ul><li>Requires <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dragon_Smithing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Dragon Smithing\">Dragon Smithing</a> perk</li>\n<li>Note that the same perk allows you to craft 24 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dragonbone_Arrow\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Dragonbone Arrow\">Dragonbone Arrows</a><sup><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dawnguard\" title=\"Skyrim:Dawnguard\">DG</a></sup> with only 1 dragon bone and 1 firewood</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by content2.uesp.net\nCached time: 20260720152105\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.027 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.068 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1506/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8197/8388608 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1997/8388608 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/1000\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 223/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   32.673      1 -total\n 26.60%    8.690      1 Template:Incomplete\n 15.77%    5.154      7 Template:Icon\n 14.48%    4.730      7 Template:ID\n 12.95%    4.230      1 Template:Notice\n 11.58%    3.784      7 Template:Anchor\n 10.03%    3.277      1 Template:Weight_Icon\n  9.67%    3.160      1 Template:DG\n  9.22%    3.013      7 Template:Icon_Abbr\n  6.33%    2.069      1 Template:Pl\n-->\n</div>"
